<subsection>
    <title>Warm Up</title>
    <activity>
        <introduction>
            <p>
                Suppose that <m>T\colon V\to W</m> is a linear transformation.
            </p>
        </introduction>
        <task>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    What is the definition of <m>\ker T</m>? How does it relate to the codomain of <m>T</m>?
                </p>
            </statement>
        </task>
        <task>
            <statement>
                <p>
